show.title: The Substitute Bride
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/F8P2vD
show.description: A lively girl is sent to the village by her stepmother and learns mystic arts there. After a playful mischief, her guru expels her. On her way back, she saves a boy from an accident—only to discover he's her arranged groom, for whom her parents have taken 100 crores. She agrees to the marriage, and despite her quirks, the boy doesn't reject her. But a strange thought lingers in his mind.
